\c 11
\nb
\v 1 Phosela isinkwa sakho phezu kobuso bamanzi\x + Isa. 32.20.\x*, ngoba uzasithola emva kwensuku ezinengi\x + Zaga 19.17.\x*.
\v 2 Nika isabelo\x + 1 Tim. 6.18,19. Mat. 5.42.\x* kwabayisikhombisa\x + Zaga 6.16.\x*, yebo, lakwabayisificaminwembili, ngoba kawazi ukuthi bubi bani obuzakuba emhlabeni\x + Efe. 5.16.\x*.
\v 3 Uba amayezi egcwele izulu, aya\add li\add*thululela emhlabeni; uba-ke isihlahla siwela ngeningizimu kumbe ngenyakatho, endaweni lapho isihlahla esiwela khona sizakuba khonapho\x + Dute. 33.23.\x*.
\v 4 Onanzelela umoya kayikuhlanyela, lalowo okhangela amayezi kayikuvuna\x + Gal. 6.9,10.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Njengoba ungazi ukuthi iyini indlela yomoya\x + 1.6. Joha. 3.8.\x*, a\add khula\add* njani amathambo esiswini sokhulelweyo, ngokunjalo kawazi umsebenzi kaNkulunkulu owenza konke\x + Jobe 10.8. Hlab. 139.13-16.\x*.
\v 6 Hlanyela inhlanyelo yakho ekuseni, lantambama ungaphumuzi isandla sakho; ngoba kawazi ukuthi yiyiphi ezaphumelela, le kumbe leyana\x + 7.18.\x*, loba zombili zizakuba zinhle ngokufananayo\x + Isa. 65.25. Ezra 3.9.\x*.
\s Izeluleko kwabatsha
\p
\v 7 Sibili, ukukhanya kumnandi; njalo kuhle emehlweni ukubona ilanga\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa uba umuntu ephila iminyaka eminengi, kathokoze ngayo yonke; kodwa kakhumbule lensuku zomnyama, ngoba zizakuba zinengi. Konke okuzayo kuyize\x + 12.1.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Thokoza, jaha, ebutsheni bakho\x + Luka 12.19.\x*, lenhliziyo yakho kayikuthokozise ensukwini zobutsha bakho\x + 12.1.\x*, uhambe endleleni zenhliziyo yakho\x + Jobe 31.7.\x* lekuboneni kwamehlo akho\x + 6.9.\x*. Kodwa yazi\x + 9.7.\x* ukuthi ngenxa yazo zonke izinto uNkulunkulu uzakuletha kusahlulelo\x + 12.14.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho susa ukudabuka enhliziyweni yakho, ukhuphe ububi enyameni yakho, ngoba ubutsha lobujaha buyize\x + 2 Kor. 7.1. 2 Tim. 2.22.\x*.
